{"tid":1549804,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解人係咁脆弱","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:19:16.000Z","uid":38958,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"760f2fc6121c31d4d58fb377cc7aa15b1e14f4eb","tid":1549804,"uid":38958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"最近發生好多事<br />\n政治 感情 家庭<br />\n無力感好重 成個人充滿負能量<br />\n為何我不可值得好點結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0eb5f96eedefd4e84d9672c0e6c7e2a92f81205","tid":1549804,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cca26ca31833bd66626604677a6d93f8fa42478e","tid":1549804,"uid":28252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:49:43.000Z","msg":"可以放低手上嘅野，<br />\n做啲會令自己開心嘅活動放鬆下先<br />\n<br />\n抖夠再Join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f539baa2ee1e103ec56e5c8ad016536136ed48","tid":1549804,"uid":43800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"頂住呀<br />\n會有好嘅結果㗎<br />\n（hug)"},{"pid":"02